quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  16,43,"Kandi mbere yawe nta bandi twigeze twohereza ngo tubahishurire ubutumwa, usibye ko babaga ari abagabo. Ngaho (yemwe babangikanyamana ba Maka)nimubaze abahawe ubumenyi (bw’ibitabo byo hambere) niba mutabizi"
  16,44,"(Twazohereje zizanye) ibimenyetso bigaragara n’ibitabo (bitagatifu). Twanaguhishuriye (yewe Muhamadi) urwibutso (Qur’an)kugira usobanurire abantu ibyo bahishuriwe, ngo ndetse no kugira ngo batekereze (ku bikubiye muri Qur’an banayisobanukirwe)"
  16,45,"Ese babandi bacuze imigambi mibisha bibwira ko batekanye ku buryo Allah atazabarigitisha mu butaka, cyangwa ko batazagerwaho n’ibihano biturutse aho batakekaga"
  16,46,"Cyangwa akabagwa gitumo bajya cyangwa bava (mu mirimo yabo), ku buryo ntaho bacikira (ibihano bya Allah)"
  16,47,"Cyangwa akabagwa gitumo bafite ubwoba (bwo kubura imitungo n’ubuzima byabo)? Mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani wanyu ni Nyiribambe, Nyirimbabazi"
  16,48,"Ese ntibabona uko ibicucucucu by’ibintu Allahyaremye bibogamira iburyo n’ibumoso byumvira Allah, ndetse binicisha bugufi (ku mategeko ye)"
  16,49,"Kandi ibiremwa byose biri mu birere, ibigenda ku isi ndetse n’abamalayika, byubamira Allah kandi ntibyishyira hejuru"
  16,50,"Bitinya Nyagasani wabyo uri hejuru, kandi bikora ibyo byategetswe"
  16,51,"Allah yaranavuze ati \"(Yemwe bantu!) Ntimuzasenge imana ebyiri. Mu by’ukuri, we (Allah) ni Imana imwe rukumbi. Bityo, nimuntinye njye njyenyine"
  16,52,Ibiri mu birere n’ibiri mu isi byose ni ibye. Ni na we ukwiye gusengwa by’ukuri. Ese mutinya undi utari Allah
  16,53,Ingabire zose mufite zituruka kwa Allah(ariko ntimumushimira). Nyamara iyo amakuba abagezeho mumutakambira mu ijwi riranguruye
  16,54,"Hanyuma yabakiza ayo makuba, bamwe muri mwe bakabangikanya Nyagasani wabo"